misc: Rarely seen on the course without a drink in his hand
biography: Martin, a formidable presence hailing from St. Laurence Golf, is set to mark his tenth appearance at the Hector Trophée in 2025. A past champion of the Hector Trophée, Martin also boasts a Victor Trophy, marking him as a force to be reckoned with both individually and as part of a pair.

Known for his jovial nature and unwavering commitment to the sport, Martin is rarely seen on the course without a drink in hand, embodying a spirit of camaraderie and enjoyment that resonates with fellow competitors and spectators alike.

With a decade of experience at the Hector Trophée under his belt, Martin's strategic acumen and skillful play make him a perennial contender for the coveted title. Opponents would be wise to note that Martin is still actively participating in Hector events.
